Description: Dual-pane SFTP/SCP/FTP/FTPS file transfer client
 BooN Transfer is a dual-pane file transfer client for SFTP, SCP, FTP and FTPS with saved sessions, a background transfer queue with pause/resume, directory synchronisation, a built-in editor, and secure credential storage via the system keyring. Built on russh and rustls — no OpenSSL, no libssh2.

